OL,3,CBonnie Tyler placed in induced coma
OL,4,Cafter emergency intestinal surgery
OL,6,FSinger Bonnie Tyler has been placed in
OL,7,Fan an induced coma to aid in her
OL,8,Frecovery from emergency intestinal
OL,9,Fsurgery.
OL,11,FThe 74-year-old Welsh star had been
OL,12,Frushed to a hospital near her home in
OL,13,FFaro, Portugal, for the procedure, her
OL,14,Fspokesperson said on Wednesday.
OL,16,FThey said on Thursday evening: "Bonnie
OL,17,Fhas been put into an induced coma by
OL,18,Fher doctors to aid her recovery.
OL,26,@xD@`OU
