OL,3,CBonnie Tyler placed in induced coma
OL,4,Cafter emergency intestinal surgery
OL,6,F"We know that you all wish her well
OL,7,Fand ask for privacy at this difficult
OL,8,Ftime please.
OL,10,F"We will issue a further statement
OL,11,Fwhen we are able to."
OL,13,FTyler, whose real name is Gaynor
OL,14,FHopkins, achieved international fame
OL,15,Fin the 1980s with the release of her
OL,16,Fsingle Total Eclipse Of The Heart,
OL,17,Fwhich shot to the top of the charts in
OL,18,Fthe UK and US.
