OL,6,FTyler is also expected to perform in
OL,7,FMalta and Germany later this month,
OL,8,Fand her upcoming tour includes shows
OL,9,Facross the UK, Austria, Hungary,
OL,10,FTurkey and Romania.
OL,12,FShe was made an MBE in 2023 for
OL,13,Fservices to music.
